</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:45_EP.jpg" class="image" title="A 7-inch 45-rpm EP."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/d1/45_EP.jpg" width="180" height="144" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:45_EP.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
