<p><a name="Common_formats" id="Common_formats"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Gramophone_record&amp;action=edit&amp;section=20" title="Edit section: Common formats">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Common formats</span></h3>
