e</a> <small>(1963)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Stereo_8" title="Stereo 8" class="mw-redirect">Stereo 8</a> <small>(1964)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/PlayTape" title="PlayTape">PlayTape</a> <small>(1966)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Mini_Cassette" title="Mini Cassette">Mini Cassette</a> <small>(1967)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Microcassette" title="Microcassette">Microcassette</a> <small>(1969)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Steno-Cassette" title="Steno-Cassette">Steno-Cassette</a> <small>(1971)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Elcaset" title="Elcaset">Elcaset</a> <small>(1976)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Cassette_single" title="Cassette single">Cassette single</a> <small>(1982)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Picocassette" title="Picocassette">Picocassette</a> <small>(1985)</small></span></p>
